</span><div id="main-tfa" class="main-box [[:Anakuhi:Yesno]] [[:Anakuhi:Yesno]]" about="#mwt4"><section data-mw-section-id="-1" id="mwDQ"><h2 class="main-header main-box-header mw-html-heading" id="ʻatikala_i_hōʻike_ʻia"><span id=".CA.BBatikala_i_h.C5.8D.CA.BBike_.CA.BBia" typeof="mw:FallbackId"></span><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anakuhi:ʻatikala_i_kēia_manawa" title="Anakuhi:ʻatikala i kēia manawa">ʻatikala i hōʻike ʻia</a></h2>
<p>ʻO ka ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi (ʻŌlelo Pelekania: Hawaiian language) — ua mea ʻōlelo makuahine a ka poʻe maoli o ka pae moku ʻo Hawaiʻi, ma laila wale nō kahi e ʻōlelo ʻia nei ia ʻōlelo, no ka mea, ʻaʻole nui ka poʻe ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi i kēia mau lā. Wahi a kekahi mau anamanaʻo aupuni, he 8,000-15,000 nā mea i hiki ke ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi. He ʻōlelo kūhelu ka ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi me ka ʻōlelo Pelekania ma ka mokuʻāina ʻo Hawaiʻi wale nō. ʻAʻole nui nā mokuʻāina ʻē aʻe me ʻelua ua ʻoi paha ʻōlelo kūhelu. aloha pe` hea `oe e o denki des ne
<br clear="all"></p>
</section></div>

<link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r98942" about="#mwt6" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles mw:Transclusion" id="mwDg" data-mw="{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"ʻaoʻao ʻaoʻao home/styles.css"},"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"ʻaoʻao ʻaoʻao home\n","href":"./Anakuhi:ʻaoʻao_ʻaoʻao_home"},"params":{"ID":{"wt":"dyk"},"poʻomanaʻo":{"wt":"Ua ʻike anei ʻoe?"},"ʻIke":{"wt":"{{Ua ʻike anei ʻoe?}}"}},"i":0}}]}"><span about="#mwt6">
</span><div id="main-dyk" class="main-box [[:Anakuhi:Yesno]] [[:Anakuhi:Yesno]]" about="#mwt6"><section data-mw-section-id="-1" id="mwDw"><h2 class="main-header main-box-header mw-html-heading" id="Ua_ʻike_anei_ʻoe?"><span id="Ua_.CA.BBike_anei_.CA.BBoe.3F" typeof="mw:FallbackId"></span>Ua ʻike anei ʻoe?</h2>
<ul><li>ʻO Hawaiʻi ke kaiaulu moku liʻiliʻi loa ma ka honua? ʻO <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Niʻihau" title="Niʻihau">Niʻihau</a> ka mokupuni hope loa i hoʻonohonoho ʻia, a ʻo ia hoʻi ka mokupuni kapu. He 170 mau kānaka wale nō e noho ana ma laila, a <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/ʻŌlelo_Hawaiʻi" title="ʻŌlelo Hawaiʻi">ʻŌlelo Hawaiʻi</a> lākou a pau.</li>
<li>E pili ana i ke kuahiwi kiʻekiʻe loa o ka honua, ʻo <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mauna_Kea" title="Mauna Kea">Mauna Kea</a>? Inā e ana ʻia mai lalo o ke kai, he 10,211 mika (33,500 kapuaʻi) kona kiʻekiʻe, ʻoi aku ma mua o <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mauna_Everest" title="Mauna Everest">Mauna Everest</a>.</li>
<li>Aia nō kekahi mau holoholona kūikawā ma Hawaiʻi? ʻO ka honu ʻea kekahi. He mea nani loa kēia honu, a he kumu hoʻohālike no nā moʻolelo Hawaiʻi he nui.</li>
<li>No ke kumu o ka inoa ʻo <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Honolulu,_Hawaiʻi" title="Honolulu, Hawaiʻi">Honolulu</a>? Ma ka ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi, ʻo kona manaʻo "wahi malu". Ua kapa ʻia pēlā no ka mea he wahi palekana a maikaʻi no nā waʻa e kū ai.</li>
<li>ʻO ka puke hemolele mua loa i unuhi ʻia i ka ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi, ʻo ia ka <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paipala" title="Paipala">Baibala</a>? Ua pau ka hana unuhi i ka makahiki 1839, a he mea nui ia no ka mālama ʻana i ka ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi.</li>
<li>E pili ana i ke mele Hawaiʻi i kākau ʻia, ʻo "<a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aloha_ʻOe" title="Aloha ʻOe">Aloha ʻOe</a>"? Na ke <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Liliʻuokalani" title="Liliʻuokalani">Aliʻiwahine Liliʻuokalani</a> i haku i kēia mele kaulana loa i ka makahiki 1878.</li>
<li>He 132 mau <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mokupuni_o_Hawaiʻi" title="Mokupuni o Hawaiʻi">mokupuni</a> ko Hawaiʻi? ʻAʻole i nohoia nā mea he nui o ia mau mokupuni, akā, he mau wahi koʻikoʻi nō lākou no nā manu kai a me nā holoholona ʻē aʻe.</li></ul>
<p><br clear="all"></p>
</section></div></td>

<div class="main-box-content"><figure class="mw-halign-center" typeof="mw:File"><a href="//haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Waihona:Hawaje-NoRedLine.jpg" class="mw-file-description" title="Satellite view of Hawaiian archipelago"><img alt="Satellite view of Hawaiian archipelago" resource="//haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Waihona:Hawaje-NoRedLine.jpg" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6b/Hawaje-NoRedLine.jpg/500px-Hawaje-NoRedLine.jpg" decoding="async" data-file-width="3600" data-file-height="2800" data-file-type="bitmap" height="389" width="500" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6b/Hawaje-NoRedLine.jpg/960px-Hawaje-NoRedLine.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6b/Hawaje-NoRedLine.jpg/1000px-Hawaje-NoRedLine.jpg 2x" class="mw-file-element"></a><figcaption>Satellite view of Hawaiian archipelago</figcaption></figure></div>

<link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r98942" about="#mwt10" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles mw:Transclusion" id="mwEw" data-mw="{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"ʻaoʻao ʻaoʻao home/styles.css"},"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"ʻaoʻao ʻaoʻao home\n","href":"./Anakuhi:ʻaoʻao_ʻaoʻao_home"},"params":{"ID":{"wt":"dyk"},"poʻomanaʻo":{"wt":"Kanaka o ka lā"},"ʻIke":{"wt":"{{Kamehameha}}"}},"i":0}}]}"><span about="#mwt10">
</span><div id="mwFA" class="main-box [[:Anakuhi:Yesno]] [[:Anakuhi:Yesno]]" about="#mwt10"><section data-mw-section-id="-1" id="mwFQ"><h2 class="main-header main-box-header mw-html-heading" id="Kanaka_o_ka_lā"><span id="Kanaka_o_ka_l.C4.81" typeof="mw:FallbackId"></span>Kanaka o ka lā</h2>
<p>ʻO <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kamehameha_I" title="Kamehameha I">Kamehameha</a> ka Mōʻī mua o ke Aupuni Hawaiʻi i hoʻokahi. Ua hānau ʻia ʻo ia ma <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kohala?action=edit&redlink=1" title="Kohala (haku ʻia ʻole)" class="new" typeof="mw:LocalizedAttrs" data-mw-i18n="{"title":{"lang":"x-page","key":"red-link-title","params":["Kohala"]}}">Kohala</a>, ma ka mokupuni ʻo Hawaiʻi, i ka makahiki 1758. He keiki hānai ʻo ia na <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Naeʻole?action=edit&redlink=1" title="Naeʻole (haku ʻia ʻole)" class="new" typeof="mw:LocalizedAttrs" data-mw-i18n="{"title":{"lang":"x-page","key":"red-link-title","params":["Naeʻole"]}}">Naeʻole</a>, a ua aʻo ʻia i ke kaua a me ke akamai aliʻi. Ua kapa ʻia ʻo ia ʻo Paiea i kona wā ʻōpio, a ua lilo ʻo ia i aliʻi koa kaulana. I ka makahiki 1782, ua hoʻomaka ʻo Kamehameha e hoʻokahi i nā mokupuni a pau o Hawaiʻi. Ua lanakila ʻo ia ma luna o <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maui" title="Maui">Maui</a>, <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Molokaʻi" title="Molokaʻi">Molokaʻi</a>, a me <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oʻahu" title="Oʻahu">Oʻahu</a> ma mua o ka makahiki 1795. Ua pau ka hoʻokahi ʻana o nā mokupuni i ka makahiki 1810 i ka hui ʻana o <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kauaʻi" title="Kauaʻi">Kauaʻi</a> a me <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Niʻihau" title="Niʻihau">Niʻihau</a> i loko o kona aupuni. Ua hoʻokumu ʻo Kamehameha i ke aupuni Hawaiʻi hou a ua hoʻoponopono i ke kānāwai, ka ʻoihana kālepa, a me ka mālama ʻana i nā kānaka. Ua make ʻo ia ma <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kailua-Kona" title="Kailua-Kona">Kailua-Kona</a> i ka lā 8 o Mei, 1819, a ua hoʻoili ʻia kona aupuni i kāna keiki, ʻo <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kamehameha_II" title="Kamehameha II">Liholiho</a>. ʻO Kamehameha ka mea i hoʻokumu i ka lālani aliʻi Kamehameha, a ua hoʻomanaʻo ʻia ʻo ia he aliʻi nui a ikaika o Hawaiʻi.
<br clear="all"></p>
</section></div>

</span><div id="mwFw" class="main-box [[:Anakuhi:Yesno]] [[:Anakuhi:Yesno]]" about="#mwt12"><section data-mw-section-id="-1" id="mwGA"><h2 class="main-header main-box-header mw-html-heading" id="E_pili_ana">E pili ana</h2>
<p>He <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Puke_noi‘i_kū‘ikena" title="Puke noi‘i kū‘ikena"> puke noi‘i kū‘ikena</a> kūnoa ʻo <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipikia" title="Wikipikia">Wikipikia</a>. E ʻoluʻolu nō, e hāʻawi mai i kāu ʻike, kāu manaʻo, a me kou leo no ke kūkulu ʻana a me ke kākoʻo ʻana mai i ka Wikipikia <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hawaiʻi" title="Hawaiʻi">Hawaiʻi</a>. He kahua pūnaewele Hawaiʻi kēia no ka hoʻoulu ʻana i ka ʻike Hawaiʻi. Inā hiki iā ʻoe ke <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/ʻōlelo_Hawaiʻi" title="ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi" class="mw-redirect">ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi</a>, e ʻoluʻolu nō, e kōkua mai a e hoʻololi i nā ʻatikala ma ʻaneʻi, a pono e haʻi aku i kou mau hoa aloha e pili ana i ka Wikipikia Hawaiʻi. E ola mau nō ka ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi a mau loa aku.</p>
<ul><li><b>Nā hua kūikawā:</b> ʻ Ā ā Ē ē Ī ī Ō ō Ū ū</li></ul>
<p><br clear="all"></p>
</section></div></td></tr>

    Mai Wikipedia

    Welina mai i Wikipikia,

    ʻencyclopedia manuahi, kahi hiki i nā mea a pau ke hoʻoponopono.

    Huli i loko o 2,961 ʻatikala

    2,961 ʻatikala a kēia Wikipikia

    ʻatikala i hōʻike ʻia

    ʻO ka ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi (ʻŌlelo Pelekania: Hawaiian language) — ua mea ʻōlelo makuahine a ka poʻe maoli o ka pae moku ʻo Hawaiʻi, ma laila wale nō kahi e ʻōlelo ʻia nei ia ʻōlelo, no ka mea, ʻaʻole nui ka poʻe ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi i kēia mau lā. Wahi a kekahi mau anamanaʻo aupuni, he 8,000-15,000 nā mea i hiki ke ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi. He ʻōlelo kūhelu ka ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi me ka ʻōlelo Pelekania ma ka mokuʻāina ʻo Hawaiʻi wale nō. ʻAʻole nui nā mokuʻāina ʻē aʻe me ʻelua ua ʻoi paha ʻōlelo kūhelu. aloha pe` hea `oe...

    Ua ʻike anei ʻoe?

    • ʻO Hawaiʻi ke kaiaulu moku liʻiliʻi loa ma ka honua? ʻO Niʻihau ka mokupuni hope loa i hoʻonohonoho ʻia, a ʻo ia hoʻi ka mokupuni kapu. He 170 mau kānaka wale nō e noho ana ma laila, a ʻŌlelo Hawaiʻi lākou a pau.
    • E pili ana i ke kuahiwi kiʻekiʻe loa o ka honua, ʻo Mauna Kea? Inā e ana ʻia mai lalo o ke kai, he 10,211 mika (33,500 kapuaʻi) kona kiʻekiʻe, ʻoi aku ma mua o Mauna Everest.
    • Aia nō kekahi mau holoholona kūikawā ma Hawaiʻi? ʻO ka honu ʻea kekahi. He mea nani loa kēia honu, a he kumu hoʻohālike no nā moʻolelo Hawaiʻi he nui.
    • No ke kumu o ka inoa ʻo Honolulu? Ma ka ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi, ʻo kona manaʻo "wahi malu". Ua kapa ʻia pēlā no ka mea he wahi palekana a maikaʻi no nā waʻa e kū ai.
    • ʻO ka puke hemolele mua loa i unuhi ʻia i ka ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi, ʻo ia ka Baibala? Ua pau ka hana unuhi i ka makahiki 1839, a he mea nui ia no ka mālama ʻana i ka ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi.
    • E pili ana i ke mele Hawaiʻi i kākau ʻia, ʻo "Aloha ʻOe"? Na ke Aliʻiwahine Liliʻuokalani i haku i kēia mele kaulana loa i ka makahiki 1878.
    • He 132 mau mokupuni ko Hawaiʻi? ʻAʻole i nohoia nā mea he nui o ia mau mokupuni, akā, he mau wahi koʻikoʻi nō lākou no nā manu kai a me nā holoholona ʻē aʻe.

    Kiʻi o ka lā


    Kanaka o ka lā

    ʻO Kamehameha ka Mōʻī mua o ke Aupuni Hawaiʻi i hoʻokahi. Ua hānau ʻia ʻo ia ma Kohala, ma ka mokupuni ʻo Hawaiʻi, i ka makahiki 1758. He keiki hānai ʻo ia na Naeʻole, a ua aʻo ʻia i ke kaua a me ke akamai aliʻi. Ua kapa ʻia ʻo ia ʻo Paiea i kona wā ʻōpio, a ua lilo ʻo ia i aliʻi koa kaulana. I ka makahiki 1782, ua hoʻomaka ʻo Kamehameha e hoʻokahi i nā mokupuni a pau o Hawaiʻi. Ua lanakila ʻo ia ma luna o Maui, Molokaʻi, a me Oʻahu ma mua o ka makahiki 1795. Ua pau ka hoʻokahi ʻana o nā mokupuni i ka makahiki 1810 i ka hui ʻana o Kauaʻi a me Niʻihau i loko o kona aupuni. Ua hoʻokumu ʻo Kamehameha i ke aupuni Hawaiʻi hou a ua hoʻoponopono i ke kānāwai, ka ʻoihana kālepa, a me ka mālama ʻana i nā kānaka. Ua make ʻo ia ma Kailua-Kona i ka lā 8 o Mei, 1819, a ua hoʻoili ʻia kona aupuni i kāna keiki, ʻo Liholiho. ʻO Kamehameha ka mea i hoʻokumu i ka lālani aliʻi Kamehameha, a ua hoʻomanaʻo ʻia ʻo ia he aliʻi nui a ikaika o Hawaiʻi.

    E pili ana

    He puke noi‘i kū‘ikena kūnoa ʻo Wikipikia. E ʻoluʻolu nō, e hāʻawi mai i kāu ʻike, kāu manaʻo, a me kou leo no ke kūkulu ʻana a me ke kākoʻo ʻana mai i ka Wikipikia Hawaiʻi. He kahua pūnaewele Hawaiʻi kēia no ka hoʻoulu ʻana i ka ʻike Hawaiʻi. Inā hiki iā ʻoe ke ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi, e ʻoluʻolu nō, e kōkua mai a e hoʻololi i nā ʻatikala ma ʻaneʻi, a pono e haʻi aku i kou mau hoa aloha e pili ana i ka Wikipikia Hawaiʻi. E ola mau nō ka ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi a mau loa aku.

Mai Wikipedia

Wikipikia,

ʻencyclopedia manuahi, kahi hiki i nā mea a pau ke hoʻoponopono.

Huli i loko o 2,961 ʻatikala

2,961 ʻatikala a kēia Wikipikia

ʻatikala i hōʻike ʻia

ʻO ka ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi (ʻŌlelo Pelekania: Hawaiian language) — ua mea ʻōlelo makuahine a ka poʻe maoli o ka pae moku ʻo Hawaiʻi, ma laila wale nō kahi e ʻōlelo ʻia nei ia ʻōlelo, no ka mea, ʻaʻole nui ka poʻe ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi i kēia mau lā. Wahi a kekahi mau anamanaʻo aupuni, he 8,000-15,000 nā mea i hiki ke ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi. He ʻōlelo kūhelu ka ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi me ka ʻōlelo Pelekania ma ka mokuʻāina ʻo Hawaiʻi wale nō. ʻAʻole nui nā mokuʻāina ʻē aʻe me ʻelua ua ʻoi paha ʻōlelo kūhelu. aloha pe` hea `oe e o denki des ne

  • ʻO Hawaiʻi ke kaiaulu moku liʻiliʻi loa ma ka honua? ʻO Niʻihau ka mokupuni hope loa i hoʻonohonoho ʻia, a ʻo ia hoʻi ka mokupuni kapu. He 170 mau kānaka wale nō e noho ana ma laila, a ʻŌlelo Hawaiʻi lākou a pau.
  • E pili ana i ke kuahiwi kiʻekiʻe loa o ka honua, ʻo Mauna Kea? Inā e ana ʻia mai lalo o ke kai, he 10,211 mika (33,500 kapuaʻi) kona kiʻekiʻe, ʻoi aku ma mua o Mauna Everest.
  • Aia nō kekahi mau holoholona kūikawā ma Hawaiʻi? ʻO ka honu ʻea kekahi. He mea nani loa kēia honu, a he kumu hoʻohālike no nā moʻolelo Hawaiʻi he nui.
  • No ke kumu o ka inoa ʻo Honolulu? Ma ka ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi, ʻo kona manaʻo "wahi malu". Ua kapa ʻia pēlā no ka mea he wahi palekana a maikaʻi no nā waʻa e kū ai.
  • ʻO ka puke hemolele mua loa i unuhi ʻia i ka ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi, ʻo ia ka Baibala? Ua pau ka hana unuhi i ka makahiki 1839, a he mea nui ia no ka mālama ʻana i ka ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi.
  • E pili ana i ke mele Hawaiʻi i kākau ʻia, ʻo "Aloha ʻOe"? Na ke Aliʻiwahine Liliʻuokalani i haku i kēia mele kaulana loa i ka makahiki 1878.
  • He 132 mau mokupuni ko Hawaiʻi? ʻAʻole i nohoia nā mea he nui o ia mau mokupuni, akā, he mau wahi koʻikoʻi nō lākou no nā manu kai a me nā holoholona ʻē aʻe.


ʻO Kamehameha ka Mōʻī mua o ke Aupuni Hawaiʻi i hoʻokahi. Ua hānau ʻia ʻo ia ma Kohala, ma ka mokupuni ʻo Hawaiʻi, i ka makahiki 1758. He keiki hānai ʻo ia na Naeʻole, a ua aʻo ʻia i ke kaua a me ke akamai aliʻi. Ua kapa ʻia ʻo ia ʻo Paiea i kona wā ʻōpio, a ua lilo ʻo ia i aliʻi koa kaulana. I ka makahiki 1782, ua hoʻomaka ʻo Kamehameha e hoʻokahi i nā mokupuni a pau o Hawaiʻi. Ua lanakila ʻo ia ma luna o Maui, Molokaʻi, a me Oʻahu ma mua o ka makahiki 1795. Ua pau ka hoʻokahi ʻana o nā mokupuni i ka makahiki 1810 i ka hui ʻana o Kauaʻi a me Niʻihau i loko o kona aupuni. Ua hoʻokumu ʻo Kamehameha i ke aupuni Hawaiʻi hou a ua hoʻoponopono i ke kānāwai, ka ʻoihana kālepa, a me ka mālama ʻana i nā kānaka. Ua make ʻo ia ma Kailua-Kona i ka lā 8 o Mei, 1819, a ua hoʻoili ʻia kona aupuni i kāna keiki, ʻo Liholiho. ʻO Kamehameha ka mea i hoʻokumu i ka lālani aliʻi Kamehameha, a ua hoʻomanaʻo ʻia ʻo ia he aliʻi nui a ikaika o Hawaiʻi.

E pili ana

He puke noi‘i kū‘ikena kūnoa ʻo Wikipikia. E ʻoluʻolu nō, e hāʻawi mai i kāu ʻike, kāu manaʻo, a me kou leo no ke kūkulu ʻana a me ke kākoʻo ʻana mai i ka Wikipikia Hawaiʻi. He kahua pūnaewele Hawaiʻi kēia no ka hoʻoulu ʻana i ka ʻike Hawaiʻi. Inā hiki iā ʻoe ke ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi, e ʻoluʻolu nō, e kōkua mai a e hoʻololi i nā ʻatikala ma ʻaneʻi, a pono e haʻi aku i kou mau hoa aloha e pili ana i ka Wikipikia Hawaiʻi. E ola mau nō ka ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi a mau loa aku.

  • Nā hua kūikawā: ʻ Ā ā Ē ē Ī ī Ō ō Ū ū

images.desc:
Kiʻi o ka lā
Satellite view of Hawaiian archipelago




Kanaka o ka lā
ʻO Kamehameha ka Mōʻī mua o ke Aupuni Hawaiʻi i hoʻokahi. Ua hānau ʻia ʻo ia ma Kohala, ma ka mokupuni ʻo Hawaiʻi, i ka makahiki 1758. He keiki hānai ʻo ia na Naeʻole, a ua aʻo ʻia i ke kaua a me ke akamai aliʻi. Ua kapa ʻia ʻo ia ʻo Paiea i kona wā ʻōpio, a ua lilo ʻo ia i aliʻi koa kaulana. I ka makahiki 1782, ua hoʻomaka ʻo Kamehameha e hoʻokahi i nā mokupuni a pau o Hawaiʻi. Ua lanakila ʻo ia ma luna o Maui, Molokaʻi, a me Oʻahu ma mua o ka makahiki 1795. Ua pau ka hoʻokahi ʻana o nā mokupuni i ka makahiki 1810 i ka hui ʻana o Kauaʻi a me Niʻihau i loko o kona aupuni. Ua hoʻokumu ʻo Kamehameha i ke aupuni Hawaiʻi hou a ua hoʻoponopono i ke kānāwai, ka ʻoihana kālepa, a me ka mālama ʻana i nā kānaka. Ua make ʻo ia ma Kailua-Kona i ka lā 8 o Mei, 1819, a ua hoʻoili ʻia kona aupuni i kāna keiki, ʻo Liholiho. ʻO Kamehameha ka mea i hoʻokumu i ka lālani aliʻi Kamehameha, a ua hoʻomanaʻo ʻia ʻo ia he aliʻi nui a ikaika o Hawaiʻi.




E pili ana
He  puke noi‘i kū‘ikena kūnoa ʻo Wikipikia. E ʻoluʻolu nō, e hāʻawi mai i kāu ʻike, kāu manaʻo, a me kou leo no ke kūkulu ʻana a me ke kākoʻo ʻana mai i ka Wikipikia Hawaiʻi. He kahua pūnaewele Hawaiʻi kēia no ka hoʻoulu ʻana i ka ʻike Hawaiʻi. Inā hiki iā ʻoe ke ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi, e ʻoluʻolu nō, e kōkua mai a e hoʻololi i nā ʻatikala ma ʻaneʻi, a pono e haʻi aku i kou mau hoa aloha e pili ana i ka Wikipikia Hawaiʻi. E ola mau nō ka ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi a mau loa aku.
Nā hua kūikawā: ʻ Ā ā Ē ē Ī ī Ō ō Ū ū

#  [Wikipikia](https://haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hawai%CA%BBi_Wikipikia "Hawaiʻi Wikipikia"),
[ ʻencyclopedia manuahi](https://haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ma%CA%BBi%CA%BBo_manuahi "Maʻiʻo manuahi"), kahi hiki i nā mea a pau ke hoʻoponopono.
[Huli i loko o 2,961 ʻatikala](https://haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Papa_nui:Huli "Papa nui:Huli")
**[2,961](https://haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Papa_nui:%CA%BBIkehelupili "Papa nui:ʻIkehelupili")** [ʻatikala](https://haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Papa_nui:AllPages "Papa nui:AllPages") a kēia Wikipikia
## [ʻatikala i hōʻike ʻia](https://haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anakuhi:%CA%BBatikala_i_k%C4%93ia_manawa "Anakuhi:ʻatikala i kēia manawa")
ʻO ka ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi (ʻŌlelo Pelekania: Hawaiian language) — ua mea ʻōlelo makuahine a ka poʻe maoli o ka pae moku ʻo Hawaiʻi, ma laila wale nō kahi e ʻōlelo ʻia nei ia ʻōlelo, no ka mea, ʻaʻole nui ka poʻe ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi i kēia mau lā. Wahi a kekahi mau anamanaʻo aupuni, he 8,000-15,000 nā mea i hiki ke ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi. He ʻōlelo kūhelu ka ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi me ka ʻōlelo Pelekania ma ka mokuʻāina ʻo Hawaiʻi wale nō. ʻAʻole nui nā mokuʻāina ʻē aʻe me ʻelua ua ʻoi paha ʻōlelo kūhelu. aloha pe` hea `oe e o denki des ne   

  * ʻO Hawaiʻi ke kaiaulu moku liʻiliʻi loa ma ka honua? ʻO [Niʻihau](https://haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ni%CA%BBihau "Niʻihau") ka mokupuni hope loa i hoʻonohonoho ʻia, a ʻo ia hoʻi ka mokupuni kapu. He 170 mau kānaka wale nō e noho ana ma laila, a [ʻŌlelo Hawaiʻi](https://haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/%CA%BB%C5%8Clelo_Hawai%CA%BBi "ʻŌlelo Hawaiʻi") lākou a pau.
  * E pili ana i ke kuahiwi kiʻekiʻe loa o ka honua, ʻo [Mauna Kea](https://haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mauna_Kea "Mauna Kea")? Inā e ana ʻia mai lalo o ke kai, he 10,211 mika (33,500 kapuaʻi) kona kiʻekiʻe, ʻoi aku ma mua o [Mauna Everest](https://haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mauna_Everest "Mauna Everest").
  * Aia nō kekahi mau holoholona kūikawā ma Hawaiʻi? ʻO ka honu ʻea kekahi. He mea nani loa kēia honu, a he kumu hoʻohālike no nā moʻolelo Hawaiʻi he nui.
  * No ke kumu o ka inoa ʻo [Honolulu](https://haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Honolulu,_Hawai%CA%BBi "Honolulu, Hawaiʻi")? Ma ka ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi, ʻo kona manaʻo "wahi malu". Ua kapa ʻia pēlā no ka mea he wahi palekana a maikaʻi no nā waʻa e kū ai.
  * ʻO ka puke hemolele mua loa i unuhi ʻia i ka ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi, ʻo ia ka [Baibala](https://haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paipala "Paipala")? Ua pau ka hana unuhi i ka makahiki 1839, a he mea nui ia no ka mālama ʻana i ka ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi.
  * E pili ana i ke mele Hawaiʻi i kākau ʻia, ʻo "[Aloha ʻOe](https://haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aloha_%CA%BBOe "Aloha ʻOe")"? Na ke [Aliʻiwahine Liliʻuokalani](https://haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lili%CA%BBuokalani "Liliʻuokalani") i haku i kēia mele kaulana loa i ka makahiki 1878.
  * He 132 mau [mokupuni](https://haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mokupuni_o_Hawai%CA%BBi "Mokupuni o Hawaiʻi") ko Hawaiʻi? ʻAʻole i nohoia nā mea he nui o ia mau mokupuni, akā, he mau wahi koʻikoʻi nō lākou no nā manu kai a me nā holoholona ʻē aʻe.

  
|  [![Satellite view of Hawaiian archipelago](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6b/Hawaje-NoRedLine.jpg/500px-Hawaje-NoRedLine.jpg)](https://haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Waihona:Hawaje-NoRedLine.jpg "Satellite view of Hawaiian archipelago")Satellite view of Hawaiian archipelago   
ʻO [Kamehameha](https://haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kamehameha_I "Kamehameha I") ka Mōʻī mua o ke Aupuni Hawaiʻi i hoʻokahi. Ua hānau ʻia ʻo ia ma [Kohala](https://haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kohala?action=edit&redlink=1 "Kohala \(haku ʻia ʻole\)"), ma ka mokupuni ʻo Hawaiʻi, i ka makahiki 1758. He keiki hānai ʻo ia na [Naeʻole](https://haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nae%CA%BBole?action=edit&redlink=1 "Naeʻole \(haku ʻia ʻole\)"), a ua aʻo ʻia i ke kaua a me ke akamai aliʻi. Ua kapa ʻia ʻo ia ʻo Paiea i kona wā ʻōpio, a ua lilo ʻo ia i aliʻi koa kaulana. I ka makahiki 1782, ua hoʻomaka ʻo Kamehameha e hoʻokahi i nā mokupuni a pau o Hawaiʻi. Ua lanakila ʻo ia ma luna o [Maui](https://haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maui "Maui"), [Molokaʻi](https://haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Moloka%CA%BBi "Molokaʻi"), a me [Oʻahu](https://haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/O%CA%BBahu "Oʻahu") ma mua o ka makahiki 1795. Ua pau ka hoʻokahi ʻana o nā mokupuni i ka makahiki 1810 i ka hui ʻana o [Kauaʻi](https://haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kaua%CA%BBi "Kauaʻi") a me [Niʻihau](https://haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ni%CA%BBihau "Niʻihau") i loko o kona aupuni. Ua hoʻokumu ʻo Kamehameha i ke aupuni Hawaiʻi hou a ua hoʻoponopono i ke kānāwai, ka ʻoihana kālepa, a me ka mālama ʻana i nā kānaka. Ua make ʻo ia ma [Kailua-Kona](https://haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kailua-Kona "Kailua-Kona") i ka lā 8 o Mei, 1819, a ua hoʻoili ʻia kona aupuni i kāna keiki, ʻo [Liholiho](https://haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kamehameha_II "Kamehameha II"). ʻO Kamehameha ka mea i hoʻokumu i ka lālani aliʻi Kamehameha, a ua hoʻomanaʻo ʻia ʻo ia he aliʻi nui a ikaika o Hawaiʻi.   

## E pili ana
He [ puke noi‘i kū‘ikena](https://haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Puke_noi%E2%80%98i_k%C5%AB%E2%80%98ikena "Puke noi‘i kū‘ikena") kūnoa ʻo [Wikipikia](https://haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipikia "Wikipikia"). E ʻoluʻolu nō, e hāʻawi mai i kāu ʻike, kāu manaʻo, a me kou leo no ke kūkulu ʻana a me ke kākoʻo ʻana mai i ka Wikipikia [Hawaiʻi](https://haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hawai%CA%BBi "Hawaiʻi"). He kahua pūnaewele Hawaiʻi kēia no ka hoʻoulu ʻana i ka ʻike Hawaiʻi. Inā hiki iā ʻoe ke [ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi](https://haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/%CA%BB%C5%8Dlelo_Hawai%CA%BBi "ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi"), e ʻoluʻolu nō, e kōkua mai a e hoʻololi i nā ʻatikala ma ʻaneʻi, a pono e haʻi aku i kou mau hoa aloha e pili ana i ka Wikipikia Hawaiʻi. E ola mau nō ka ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi a mau loa aku.

#  Wikipikia⟨41⟩,
 ʻencyclopedia manuahi⟨42⟩, kahi hiki i nā mea a pau ke hoʻoponopono.
Huli i loko o 2,961 ʻatikala⟨10⟩
**2,961⟨43⟩** ʻatikala⟨44⟩ a kēia Wikipikia
## ʻatikala i hōʻike ʻia⟨45⟩
ʻO ka ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi (ʻŌlelo Pelekania: Hawaiian language) — ua mea ʻōlelo makuahine a ka poʻe maoli o ka pae moku ʻo Hawaiʻi, ma laila wale nō kahi e ʻōlelo ʻia nei ia ʻōlelo, no ka mea, ʻaʻole nui ka poʻe ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi i kēia mau lā. Wahi a kekahi mau anamanaʻo aupuni, he 8,000-15,000 nā mea i hiki ke ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi. He ʻōlelo kūhelu ka ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi me ka ʻōlelo Pelekania ma ka mokuʻāina ʻo Hawaiʻi wale nō. ʻAʻole nui nā mokuʻāina ʻē aʻe me ʻelua ua ʻoi paha ʻōlelo kūhelu. aloha pe` hea `oe e o denki des ne   

  * ʻO Hawaiʻi ke kaiaulu moku liʻiliʻi loa ma ka honua? ʻO Niʻihau⟨46⟩ ka mokupuni hope loa i hoʻonohonoho ʻia, a ʻo ia hoʻi ka mokupuni kapu. He 170 mau kānaka wale nō e noho ana ma laila, a ʻŌlelo Hawaiʻi⟨47⟩ lākou a pau.
  * E pili ana i ke kuahiwi kiʻekiʻe loa o ka honua, ʻo Mauna Kea⟨48⟩? Inā e ana ʻia mai lalo o ke kai, he 10,211 mika (33,500 kapuaʻi) kona kiʻekiʻe, ʻoi aku ma mua o Mauna Everest⟨49⟩.
  * Aia nō kekahi mau holoholona kūikawā ma Hawaiʻi? ʻO ka honu ʻea kekahi. He mea nani loa kēia honu, a he kumu hoʻohālike no nā moʻolelo Hawaiʻi he nui.
  * No ke kumu o ka inoa ʻo Honolulu⟨50⟩? Ma ka ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi, ʻo kona manaʻo "wahi malu". Ua kapa ʻia pēlā no ka mea he wahi palekana a maikaʻi no nā waʻa e kū ai.
  * ʻO ka puke hemolele mua loa i unuhi ʻia i ka ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi, ʻo ia ka Baibala⟨51⟩? Ua pau ka hana unuhi i ka makahiki 1839, a he mea nui ia no ka mālama ʻana i ka ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi.
  * E pili ana i ke mele Hawaiʻi i kākau ʻia, ʻo "Aloha ʻOe⟨52⟩"? Na ke Aliʻiwahine Liliʻuokalani⟨53⟩ i haku i kēia mele kaulana loa i ka makahiki 1878.
  * He 132 mau mokupuni⟨54⟩ ko Hawaiʻi? ʻAʻole i nohoia nā mea he nui o ia mau mokupuni, akā, he mau wahi koʻikoʻi nō lākou no nā manu kai a me nā holoholona ʻē aʻe.

  
|  ![Satellite view of Hawaiian archipelago⟨55⟩](https://haw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Waihona:Hawaje-NoRedLine.jpg "Satellite view of Hawaiian archipelago")Satellite view of Hawaiian archipelago   
ʻO Kamehameha⟨56⟩ ka Mōʻī mua o ke Aupuni Hawaiʻi i hoʻokahi. Ua hānau ʻia ʻo ia ma Kohala⟨57⟩, ma ka mokupuni ʻo Hawaiʻi, i ka makahiki 1758. He keiki hānai ʻo ia na Naeʻole⟨58⟩, a ua aʻo ʻia i ke kaua a me ke akamai aliʻi. Ua kapa ʻia ʻo ia ʻo Paiea i kona wā ʻōpio, a ua lilo ʻo ia i aliʻi koa kaulana. I ka makahiki 1782, ua hoʻomaka ʻo Kamehameha e hoʻokahi i nā mokupuni a pau o Hawaiʻi. Ua lanakila ʻo ia ma luna o Maui⟨59⟩, Molokaʻi⟨60⟩, a me Oʻahu⟨61⟩ ma mua o ka makahiki 1795. Ua pau ka hoʻokahi ʻana o nā mokupuni i ka makahiki 1810 i ka hui ʻana o Kauaʻi⟨62⟩ a me Niʻihau⟨46⟩ i loko o kona aupuni. Ua hoʻokumu ʻo Kamehameha i ke aupuni Hawaiʻi hou a ua hoʻoponopono i ke kānāwai, ka ʻoihana kālepa, a me ka mālama ʻana i nā kānaka. Ua make ʻo ia ma Kailua-Kona⟨63⟩ i ka lā 8 o Mei, 1819, a ua hoʻoili ʻia kona aupuni i kāna keiki, ʻo Liholiho⟨64⟩. ʻO Kamehameha ka mea i hoʻokumu i ka lālani aliʻi Kamehameha, a ua hoʻomanaʻo ʻia ʻo ia he aliʻi nui a ikaika o Hawaiʻi.   

## E pili ana
He  puke noi‘i kū‘ikena⟨65⟩ kūnoa ʻo Wikipikia⟨66⟩. E ʻoluʻolu nō, e hāʻawi mai i kāu ʻike, kāu manaʻo, a me kou leo no ke kūkulu ʻana a me ke kākoʻo ʻana mai i ka Wikipikia Hawaiʻi⟨67⟩. He kahua pūnaewele Hawaiʻi kēia no ka hoʻoulu ʻana i ka ʻike Hawaiʻi. Inā hiki iā ʻoe ke ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi⟨68⟩, e ʻoluʻolu nō, e kōkua mai a e hoʻololi i nā ʻatikala ma ʻaneʻi, a pono e haʻi aku i kou mau hoa aloha e pili ana i ka Wikipikia Hawaiʻi. E ola mau nō ka ʻōlelo Hawaiʻi a mau loa aku.
